headline: Old Dominion Freight Line to Webcast Second Quarter 2025 Conference Call
summary: THOMASVILLE, N.C., July 02, 2025--Old Dominion Freight Line, Inc. (Nasdaq: ODFL) announced today that it plans to release its second quarter 2025 financial results before opening of trading on Wednesday, July 30, 2025. The Company will also hold a conference call to discuss its financial results and outlook at 10:00 a.m. (Eastern Time) on Wednesday, July 30, 2025.
